angement et nettoyage ;<br \\/>- Respect des r\\u00e8gles de s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 ;<br \\/>- Respect du mat\\u00e9riel.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"56e25b7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/worpresstest\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/07\\/Cap.png\",\"id\":190,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"f709845\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Malick TRAORE\",\"title_color\":\"#080909\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"66d9857\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Technicien FabLab Solidaire Orange<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
